    {
      "repository": "gordolio/Trio",
      "number": 1223,
      "title": "Remove unused convertGlucose function",
      "body": "This PR removes an unused function from the core determine basal logic in oref-swift: `convertGlucose`. In the original JS implementation, several output properties and reason string values are run through a `convert_bg` function that converts the glucose value to `mmol` based on the `profile.outUnits` value.\r\n\r\nHowever, `profile.outUnits` is always in `.mgdl`, and should always be in `.mgdl` so we should remove this function. The path goes:\r\n- The convert function branches based on the value of `profile.outUnits`\r\n- `profile.outUnits` is set from `bgTarget.userPreferredUnits`\r\n- all of the write paths for the file that saves the `bgTarget` value store these values as mg/dl and hard code `userPreferredUnits` to `.mgdl`.\r\n\r\nUnit tests still pass with this change.",
      "labels": [],
      "url": "https://github.com/nightscout/Trio/pull/1223",
      "mergedAt": "2026-06-20T23:14:31Z"
    },
    {
      "repository": "nightscout/Trio",
      "number": 1223,
      "title": "Remove unused convertGlucose function",
      "body": "This PR removes an unused function from the core determine basal logic in oref-swift: `convertGlucose`. In the original JS implementation, several output properties and reason string values are run through a `convert_bg` function that converts the glucose value to `mmol` based on the `profile.outUnits` value.\r\n\r\nHowever, `profile.outUnits` is always in `.mgdl`, and should always be in `.mgdl` so we should remove this function. The path goes:\r\n- The convert function branches based on the value of `profile.outUnits`\r\n- `profile.outUnits` is set from `bgTarget.userPreferredUnits`\r\n- all of the write paths for the file that saves the `bgTarget` value store these values as mg/dl and hard code `userPreferredUnits` to `.mgdl`.\r\n\r\nUnit tests still pass with this change.",
      "labels": [],
      "url": "https://github.com/nightscout/Trio/pull/1223",
      "mergedAt": "2026-06-20T23:14:31Z"
    },
